author: jeremias
msg: Added an option to disable the default sRGB profile in PDF output for those who don't care about color fidelity, but care about PDF file size. Note that this option is not possible if PDF/A, PDF/X or an output profile is used. Makes simple PDFs about 4KB smaller. Ha!
